<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <link href="~/css/about.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <title>About Us</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #ADD8E6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

       
        .container1 {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .section {
            margin-bottom: 40px;

        }

            .section h2 {
                background-color: #333;
                color: white;
                padding: 10px;
                border-radius: 8px;
            }

            .section p {
                line-height: 1.6;
            }

        .team {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: space-around;
        }

        .team-member {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 10px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
            flex-basis: 30%;

        }

            .team-member img {
                border-radius: 50%;
                width: 100px;
                height: 100px;
            }

            .team-member h3 {
                margin: 10px 0 5px 0;
            }

            .team-member p {
                margin: 5px 0;
                color: #777;
            }

        
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <br />
        <h1 style="text-align:center">About Us</h1>
    
    
    <div class="container1">
        <div class="section">
            <h2 style="width:200px">Our Mission</h2>
            <p>Our mission is to provide the best services to our customers and ensure satisfaction in every aspect of our business. We strive for excellence and aim to exceed expectations in everything we do.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="section">
            <h2 style="width:200px">Our Vision</h2>
            <p>We envision a world where our services make a significant impact on the lives of our customers, helping them achieve their goals and dreams. We are committed to innovation, growth, and continuous improvement.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="section">
            <h2 style="width:200px">Our Team</h2>
            <div class="team">
                <div class="team-member">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/100" alt="Team Member 1">
                    <h3>Nguyen Le Hoai</h3>
                    <p>DESIGN</p>
                </div>
                <div class="team-member">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/100" alt="Team Member 2">
                    <h3>Nguyen Viet Tinh</h3>
                    <p>DEVERLOP</p>
                </div>
                <div class="team-member">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/100" alt="Team Member 3">
                    <h3>Nguyen Phan Ngoc Thuan</h3>
                    <p>TEST</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
</body>
